Why Choose Quick Pass?

Quick Pass Traffic School is your one-stop shop for the Florida 12-hour Advanced Driver Improvement (ADI) course. The program is fully approved by the Florida DHSMV and designed to help you meet state requirements quickly and conveniently.

Course Overview

Comprehensive curriculum designed to improve your driving skills and knowledge

Traffic Laws & Regulations

Review Florida’s key traffic laws and learn how to drive safely and responsibly.

Defensive Driving Techniques

Build stronger driving habits that help you avoid accidents and violations.

Hazard Recognition & Avoidance

Recognize common risks on Florida’s roads and learn how to handle them.

Human Factors in Driving

Understand how attention, mood, and reaction time affect your performance.

Crash Prevention Strategies

Discover proven ways to stay alert, reduce risks, and prevent collisions.

Traffic Violation Consequences
